#. RonivansLegacy_ChemicalProcessing.STRINGS.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.CHEMICAL_LIQUID_BOILER.NAME
msgctxt "RonivansLegacy_ChemicalProcessing.STRINGS.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.CHEMICAL_LIQUID_BOILER.NAME"
